PrecisAuthority (a) to enter into an AGREEMENT with the Government of the NORTHWEST TERRITORIES and an Inuit Organization to be designated by the Tungavik Federation of Nunavut which will grant that Organization exclusive possession of certain Inuit-owned lands as provided for in the Nunavut Land Claims Agreement, and (b) to designate a person to approve the descriptive map plans of the Nunavut Settlement Area on behalf of the Federal Government.
Attachments
precis:
Authority (a) to enter into an AGREEMENT with the Government of the
NORTHWEST TERRITORIES and an Inuit Organization to be designated by the
Tungavik Federation of Nunavut which will grant that Organization exclusive
possession of certain Inuit-owned lands as provided for in the Nunavut Land
Claims Agreement, and (b) to designate a person to approve the descriptive
map plans of the Nunavut Settlement Area on behalf of the Federal
Government.
